headline: Wells Fargo Bank Decreases Prime Rate to 7.00 Percent
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, October 29, 2025--Wells Fargo Bank, N.A., said today it is decreasing its prime rate to 7.00 percent from 7.25 percent, effective tomorrow, Oct. 30, 2025.
